description: Alexander Lukashenko says a group of those who dispute the election results are trying to seize power.
title: Belarus unrest: President Lukashenko accuses opposition of staging coup
title_page: Belarus unrest: President Lukashenko accuses opposition of staging coup - BBC News
maintext: In a televised meeting, Mr Lukashenko said the group's aim was clear: "They demand nothing less than the transfer of power. We see it unequivocally: it is an attempt to seize power... with all the consequences that come with it."
